    <tags>ai cli development terminal coding assistant</tags>
    <summary>Free, privacy-first AI coding assistant for the terminal</summary>
    <description>
Vibe CLI is a free, privacy-first AI coding assistant for the terminal with advanced chat, code generation, refactoring, debugging, test authoring, git automation, and autonomous agent workflows powered by OpenRouter's free models.

Features:
- Interactive chat with AI assistant
- Code generation from natural language
- Intelligent refactoring
- Debug assistance
- Test generation
- Git integration
- Autonomous agent mode
- Enhanced interactive features (visual feedback, file browser, command history)
    </description>
